TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_SEQ_00Qhoterl Pasol knows that it pays to be prepared.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.

TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_SEQ_00 Schwierigkeitsanpassung (Job/Klasse darf nicht gewechselt werden)

Qhoterl Pasol möchte für Notfälle vorsorgen.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_SEQ_01<tab>Deliver the requested items to Qhoterl Pasol.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_SEQ_01<tab>Qhoterl Pasol die gewünschte Ware bringen

source: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E4E80511 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Mine splendid chalcanthite at the Husk)) ((Deliver the splendid chalcanthite to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80512 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Gather splendid tarantulas at the Husk)) ((Deliver the splendid tarantulas to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80513 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Catch a splendid poison catfish at Mjrl's Tears)) ((Deliver the splendid poison catfish to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) (()) /var>)) /var>)) /var>.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E4E80511 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Beim Verlorenen Juwel <var 28 ((Item)) E8060A /var> finden)) ((Qhoterl Pasol den <var 28 ((Item)) E8060A /var> bringen)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80512 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Beim Verlorenen Juwel <var 32 ((Item)) 06E806030502 /var> ernten)) ((Qhoterl Pasol <var 32 ((Item)) 03E806030502 /var> bringen)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80513 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((In Mjrls Tränen <var 32 ((Item)) 02E806020502 /var> fangen)) ((Qhoterl Pasol <var 32 ((Item)) 02E806020502 /var> bringen)) /var>)) (()) /var>)) /var>)) /var>

source: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>Thanks to the protective enchantments of the Night's Blessed, we may carry out our exploration without fear of fiends. Of course, enchantments are wont to lose effect over time, and when that happens, we must be prepared to protect ourselves.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>Dank Schutzamulette von Untertanen der Nacht können Bestien Qitari nichts anhaben! Aber manchmal verlieren Schutzamulette Wirkung.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>To that end, I intend to concoct a potent poison, and I would be most grateful if you could obtain an ingredient for me.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>Brauchen Schutz vor solchen Notfällen! Zur Verteidigung wollen Grabende Pfoten Gift herstellen!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_010<tab>Chalcanthite is what I require, and it can be mined at the Husk. Three clusters or so should be suitable for our purposes.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_010<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, bringst du für Gift drei <var 32 ((Item)) 06F27353030502 /var>, ja? Findest du sicher bei Verlorenem Juwel!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_020<tab>Tarantulas are what I require, and they can be found at the Husk. Three or so should be suitable for our purposes.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_020<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, bringst du für Gift drei <var 32 ((Item)) 06F2736D030502 /var>, ja? Findest du sicher bei Verlorenem Juwel!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_030<tab>A poison catfish is what I require, and it can be caught at Mjrl's Tears with a fruit worm on your hook. A single creature should be suitable for our purposes.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_030<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, bringst du für Gift <var 32 ((Item)) 06F27387020502 /var>, ja? Fängst du ganz leicht mit <var 32 ((Item)) 06F26BBE020402 /var> in Mjrls Tränen!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_040<tab>Please bring me the three chalcanthite clusters I require to make my poison. Remember, they can be mined at the Husk.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_040<tab>Bring für Gift drei <var 32 ((Item)) 06F27353030502 /var>. Findest du sicher bei Verlorenem Juwel!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_050<tab>Please bring me the three tarantulas I require to make my poison. Remember, they can be found at the Husk.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_050<tab>Bring für Gift drei <var 32 ((Item)) 06F2736D030502 /var>. Findest du sicher bei Verlorenem Juwel!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_060<tab>Please bring me the poison catfish I require to make my poison. Remember, they can be caught at Mjrl's Tears with a fruit worm on your hook.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_060<tab>Bring für Gift <var 32 ((Item)) 06F27387020502 /var>. Fängst du ganz leicht mit <var 32 ((Item)) 06F26BBE020402 /var> in Mjrls Tränen!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_070<tab>Pleased for your return, good <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Were you successful in procuring the ingredient I requested?

TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_080<tab>Splendid, my thanks for your kind cooperation. Lest you wonder, the poison works by robbing fiends of their movement. Applied to dart tips, it won't slay outright, but it will afford us an opportunity to retreat to safety.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_080<tab>Ah, sehr gut! Daraus machen Qitari Gift für Pfeile. So werden Bestien gelähmt, bevor sie mampfen können!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_081<tab>Of course, I pray that our people needn't resort to such measures at all. May merciful Dalan ever bless us and keep us safe from harm.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ109_03814_QHOTERLPASOL_000_081<tab>Ich hoffe, dass Grabende Pfoten sie nie einsetzen müssen, aber man weiß ja nie. Beten allein hilft nicht immer!
